data.description: This home is situated on a double mature lot.  Close to parks and elementary school.  Enjoy the relaxing on the front deck or in the evenings enjoy a fire in the firepit.  Nicely landscaped.  Shed in backyard will convey.  Now to this home, it offers 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The master bedroom offers full bath, walkin closet.  The currently used den/office could be use a dining area.  Laundry room is a great size and also offers a utility sink, cabinet and folding area.  Mud room off the back of the home leads to the oversize lot with brick fire pit,  mature trees and shed.    Everything throughout the home is updated.  All kitchen appliances will transfer.  This is a must see.
